                            jump to other results
                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" htag="li" id="atlanticcity_sng_1" hclass="sense"><span class="sensetop" htag="span" hclass="sensetop"><span class="def" hclass="def" htag="span">a city on the coast in the American state of <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/new-jersey" title="New Jersey definition"><span class="ndv">New Jersey</span></a>. It is popular with tourists and contains many <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/casino#casino_topg_1" title="casinos definition"><span class="ndv">casinos</span></a> <span class="gloss" htag="span" hclass="gloss">(= <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/gambling" title="gambling definition"><span class="ndv">gambling</span></a> clubs)</span> where people can <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/gamble_1" title="gamble definition"><span class="ndv">gamble</span></a> legally. The city has a famous Boardwalk <span class="gloss" hclass="gloss" htag="span">(= a wide path made of wood)</span> along the edge of the sea, and the names of some of its streets were used for the US version of the game <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/monopoly#monopoly_sng_3" title="Monopoly definition"><span class="ndv">Monopoly</span></a>.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
